languages.text: "Не тревожься о них. Мы пока не знаем их имен, но Неумирающий ведает имя каждого".
languages.translation_comment:
Speaker Kibellah
Argenta: "On Salis Prime we slew another worshipper of the Final Dawn... How many more such heretics are scattered across the Expanse? How many more are preparing to strike?"

languages.text: "Do not worry about them. We do not know their names yet, but the Undying One knows all names."
